data-triple-N3.o: "Bolton Wanderers Football Club is an English professional football club based in Horwich in the Metropolitan Borough of Bolton, who play in the Football League Championship. The club is currently competing in the 2012–13 Championship, having been relegated from the Premier League at the end of last season, after finishing 18th. The club was formed as Christ Church Football Club in 1874, and adopted its current name in 1877."@en
